# Frontend Architecture

See [apps/web/AGENTS.md](mdc:apps/web/AGENTS.md).

- Layout: [apps/web/app/layout.tsx](mdc:apps/web/app/layout.tsx)
- Providers: [apps/web/components/providers.tsx](mdc:apps/web/components/providers.tsx)
- tRPC browser client: [apps/web/trpc/client.tsx](mdc:apps/web/trpc/client.tsx)
- tRPC server: [apps/web/trpc/server.tsx](mdc:apps/web/trpc/server.tsx) — use `trpcCaller` in RSC; `trpc` proxy for client components

## Guidelines

- Prefer Server Components; client components only when needed.
- RSC data: `const api = await trpcCaller()` then `api.user.getUser()` — no HTTP loopback.
- Client hooks: `trpc` from `@/trpc/client` (or generated hooks), not raw fetch to `/api/trpc`.
- Shared UI: [packages/ui/src](mdc:packages/ui/src).
- Secrets stay server-side; only `NEXT_PUBLIC_*` on the client.
